OL,3,CUnion calls on Chancellor to freeze
OL,4,Cduty on Scotch whisky
OL,6,FRachel Reeves has been urged to freeze
OL,7,Falcohol duty on whisky in a bid to
OL,8,Fsave jobs and boost the economy.
OL,10,FGMB Scotland, one of the largest
OL,11,Funions in the industry, has written to
OL,12,Fthe Chancellor warning her not to
OL,13,Fraise taxes on spirits.
OL,15,FIn the letter sent ahead of next
OL,16,Fmonth's budget Louise Gilmour, the
OL,17,Funion's general secretary, called for
OL,18,Fa freeze on the duty until the next
OL,19,Felection in 2029.
