OL,3,CUnion calls on Chancellor to freeze
OL,4,Cduty on Scotch whisky
OL,6,FShe said the move would immediately
OL,7,Fhelp support exports and jobs while
OL,8,Fbolstering the Treasury's revenues in
OL,9,Fthe long-term.
OL,11,FMs Gilmour welcomed the UK
OL,12,FGovernment's trade deals with major
OL,13,FScotch importers, including India, but
OL,14,Fsaid the benefits would take time to
OL,15,Fbe seen as whisky producers report
OL,16,Fslowing international sales.
