OL,3,CUnion calls on Chancellor to freeze
OL,4,Cduty on Scotch whisky
OL,6,FThe industry faced a 10.1% duty
OL,7,Fincrease two years ago under the
OL,8,FConservative Government, and last year
OL,9,Fthe Chancellor chose to raise it again
OL,10,Fby the higher RPI rate of inflation.
OL,12,FThe Scotch Whisky Association (SWA)
OL,13,Fwarned last year that the previous
OL,14,Fincrease resulted in whisky revenue
OL,15,Ffalling by hundreds of millions of
OL,16,Fpounds, ultimately leading to a lower
OL,17,Fintake by HMRC.
