OL,3,CUnion calls on Chancellor to freeze
OL,4,Cduty on Scotch whisky
OL,6,F"A multi-year freeze on spirits duty
OL,7,Fwould provide much-needed stability
OL,8,Ffor Scottish and UK businesses and the
OL,9,Fcommunities that rely on the industry,
OL,10,Fallowing them to grow and invest at a
OL,11,Ftime when all businesses are facing
OL,12,Fpressure."
OL,14,FA Treasury spokesperson said: "The
OL,15,FChancellor has been clear that at
OL,16,FBudget she will strike the right
OL,17,Fbalance between making sure we have
OL,18,Fenough money to fund our public
OL,19,Fservices and ensuring we can bring
OL,20,Fgrowth and investment to businesses.
