OL,3,CUnion calls on Chancellor to freeze
OL,4,Cduty on Scotch whisky
OL,6,F"Our distilleries are vital to
OL,7,FBritain's economy, so we're making it
OL,8,Feasier for them to thrive: no export
OL,9,Fduty, lower licensing fees, reduced
OL,10,Ftariffs, and a cap on corporation tax.
OL,12,F"Whisky and gin exporters are some of
OL,13,Fthe biggest winners from our recent
OL,14,FIndia trade deal, cutting tariffs from
OL,15,F150% to 40% and boosting whisky
OL,16,Fexports by #1 billion."
